===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|charcole}}, from {{m|enm|charren||to change, turn}} + {{m|enm|cole||coal}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|cierran||to change, turn}} + {{m|ang|col||coal}}, equivalent to {{compound|char|coal|lang=en}}. More at [[ajar]], [[coal]].

